{"tid":125393,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"買車疑似畀人呃左","createTime":"2017-02-18T12:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T01:35:22.000Z","uid":53581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"928f4fecc1818e633a78bfb821baa39e0a4cacae","tid":125393,"uid":53581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排屋企人想買架二手車 上網見到有啱嘅車就約出黎睇<br />\n<br />\n尋晚我爸爸出左去睇車同見個車主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我爸爸見佢幾啱傾所以好信佢 最後仲落左10000訂俾佢<br />\n<br />\n但今日打左好多次畀佢 無聽 剛才再打去熄埋電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有抄底身份證 有佢車牌 有份文件簽左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n聽日會報警 但諗唔明點解會咁樣呃法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想巴絲幫手分析下 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397cfe41473888ff9eee1b08cac27fa30b3d6ecc","tid":125393,"uid":63194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"未驗車就落訂?"},{"pid":"bcc2ac7b737f010e24eefb3f3a8d6e84e3cbf0d6","tid":125393,"uid":53581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未驗車就落訂?</blockquote><br />\n佢話係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1bbd85e6a1b5ca90c116802ad44868185b31b9","tid":125393,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"冇證冇據"},{"pid":"176fa7004f296308d6ea5884c7e6b95cfe52022a","tid":125393,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:24:01.000Z","msg":"現金俾一萬？定ATM"},{"pid":"9cb65d2c8b4a616c88b4ba5a5b08c96f3f5e4521","tid":125393,"uid":53581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"佢話就