證 有車牌 簽左文件都會咁</blockquote><br />\n咩文件？<br />\n臨時約？</blockquote><br />\n我啱啱睇左嗰份嘢 似係上網下載落黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係有雙方嘅簽名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n簽名係人都識架啦<br />\n有無講時限內交唔到車/驗車唔合格就可以有權拒買？唔賣就賠訂？"},{"pid":"c8d1472f6bf1a0029fea33cad71c66b13c6e44fa","tid":125393,"uid":17759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T22:56:55.000Z","msg":"落咁撚多訂係咪傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fffb467bcf10970b20c4487b8ae7504688c3ee","tid":125393,"uid":37760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T23:44:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27c0294c76c84ef0333ca2ea09d87722cd38840e","tid":125393,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T00:54:50.000Z","msg":"買新車就話啫<br />\n買二手落咁重訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed4d294c1cfbde3ad99136c275322b92b103fa4","tid":125393,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"睇運，差佬未必幫你，除非條友呃左十個八個"},{"pid":"3aeb2008d54c561a540b576b202329b28223f5e2","tid":125393,"uid":53520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:21:24.000Z","msg":"我估樓主老豆係睇岩車，跟手人地又游說下佢話轉頭重約左幾多個人睇，又準備上架咁，叫佢落訂就推左佢地，btw 簽左臨約有身份證應該有得追?<br />\n<br />\n利申 9估"},{"pid":"bfda8d6bf10dffc44b67097574b3fcae99ec6391","tid":125393,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買新車就話啫<br />\n買二手落咁重訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廿萬新車都係2/3萬  二手都比一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59c5670f67fcd73dda558369e5151292f933b76","tid":125393,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:43:10.000Z","msg":